name: Rock Petir!
description:
This is my previous work for Komunal before the pandemic. One of the most intense performances with a great vibe from their fans.

This series is my first minting, and officially and legally had a permission from the band for supporting my work during this pandemic. 

Komunal are Doddy Hamson (vocal), Arief Snik (bass), Unwar Sadat (guitar), Rezha Ai (drum). They are known as one of Indonesian heavy metal monsters with loyal fans.
